thread.title: Julie McGrath
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Julie McGrath

author: Julie McGrath
title: Julie McGrath
text: I regularly order the canned sockeye salmon. I love it for its taste and meatiness. This product requires minimum preparation and it will keep for a long time. It's easy to order on-line and I receive my product at my door step within days. I cannot say anything negative about Vital Choice. There a great company to do business with.
